{
  "texts": [
    "The experimental results are shown in Table 7.From Table 7, it shows that: (1) DE3TC w/o Context performs best, outperforms other baselines on 20% and 30% of training data, and is competitive on 10%.",
    "However, the complete DE3TC achieved sub-optimal performance on 20% and 30%, still significantly better than other baselines.",
    "An interesting phenomenon is that DE3TC w/o Context performs better than DE3TC.",
    "When only a small amount of data is available for training, the Clue captures the event information in the sentence.",
    "Under low-resource conditions, the model does not have enough samples to learn the semantic information of event types, and context containing other events' semantics becomes noise."
  ]
}